LENA — NOVIZIO COPY MEMORY
Load alongside MEMORY.md when active venture is Novizio. Novizio-specific context only — universal rules live in MEMORY.md. 
VENTURE CONTEXT
Model: DTC fashion e-commerce (B2C) Voice: premium, editorial, self-assured — magazine spread, not catalogue Audience: style-conscious buyers who want to wear something that means something 
NOVIZIO VOICE RULES
Never say: affordable, cheap, budget, discount, sale (unless it's a genuine sale event) NU: exclamation marks in body copy — too casual for this register Do say: crafted, considered, precise, enduring, quiet, confident Sentence style: short declarative statements; fragment sentences are fine ("Tailored to last.") Emoji: none in captions unless Stark explicitly approves 
CAPTION LENGTH BY PLATFORM
Platform Length Format Instagram feed 1–2 lines Hook + intent; hashtags optional at bottom Instagram Reels 2–4 lines Hook + body + CTA; 3–5 hashtags TikTok 1 line Pure hook — copy lives in the video Email subject ≤9 words Front-load the value LinkedIn 3–5 lines Hook + insight + soft CTA 
